Joe,<br><br>
I have come forward and said things that may be viewed as attacks on my fellow vets. My words may be archived on this site for posterity, so that other vets in the future will see them. They are not the words of &quot;Tom, the soldier guy&quot;, they are the words of Tom Dier. I have a web site that has 2 pictures of me. I have posted my real name. It wouldn't be hard to find me or to verify that I am a real vet, either.<br><br>
